Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,CARGO. Last-mile expeditionary delivery in 60 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Forward depot to eight dispersed squads — thirty kilometers,\Nforty-eight hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight squads alpha through hotel. Three named threat zones — UAS,\Nsniper, IED-cleared corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Operator types one push request — agent fires real tool calls on a\NKamiwaza-deployed model.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,list_squad_positions, compute_route, check_threat_overlay,\Ncompare_options — streamed live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Three options ranked. Recommended pulses neon green — animated route\Nover the dark map.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL — same code, on-prem inference, 100% data\Ncontainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,CARGO. Built on the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
